text: Got my drone fitted with Minimosd. Pretty cool seeing the artificial horizon. A bit laggier than expected though.
Best thing is having a menu controllable on your remote to tune pids and other cleanflight settings.
Am able to help you setup yours now. Kinda convoluted wiring the system though.
Did actually figure out that moving/stationary vehicles counted as a covered structure. So long as we don't fly over unprotected non-participants we are fine.
Been hearing good things about betaflight... Might be worth looking into it.
